snippet.title: Witchy Life Story Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Don’t get kicked out of training in this narrative sim! Grow ingredients and craft spells to help the village of Flora prepare for the harvest festival (or not). Make some friends, and get a date (or not). Figure out your life (or not). Growing up is hard, OK?

Wishlist & Follow on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1427340/Witchy_Life_Story/
